<Layout title="Real Estate Agent Commission Structures in Queensland: Tiered, Flat, and Percentage Explained | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Queensland sellers can be quoted commission as a flat percentage, a tiered scale, or a fixed dollar fee. Each structure changes what your agent is incentivised to do. Here is how they work and which suits which seller." draft={draft}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
